| # | Identity | নাম |
|---|----------|------|
| 1 | C(n,k) = C(n,n-k) | Symmetry Rule |
| 2 | C(n,k) = C(n-1,k-1) + C(n-1,k) | Pascal's Identity |
| 3 | k*C(n,k) = n*C(n-1,k-1) | Absorption Identity |
| 4 | Sum C(n,k) (k=0..n) = 2^n | Total Subsets |
| 5 | Sum (-1)^k * C(n,k) (k=0..n) = 0 | Alternating Sum |
| 6 | Sum C(n,odd) = 2^(n-1) | Even/Odd Sum |
| 7 | Sum C(i,k) (i=k..n) = C(n+1,k+1) | Hockey-Stick |
| 8 | Sum C(m,k) (m=0..n) = C(n+1,k+1) | Sum over Upper Index |
| 9 | Sum C(m,k)*C(n,r-k) (k=0..r) = C(m+n,r) | Vandermonde |
| 10 | Sum C(n,k)^2 (k=0..n) = C(2n,n) | Sum of Squares |
